Home »
				
									  STRATEGY					 

STRATEGY
 
 







Strategy


Focus Equity Strategy
Broad Run applies its investment approach and process to managing a single strategy, the Focus Equity Strategy.




Objective:

Seeks long-term capital appreciation while incurring a low risk of permanent capital loss



Summary:

Concentrated and low turnover portfolio of what we believe to be high quality, growth-oriented companies, selected using fundamental analysis and valuation discipline



Vehicle(s):

Separate Accounts; Mutual Fund (via subadvisory)



To learn more, please see the strategy Fact Sheet, or contact us.
 
 





Download Fact Sheet







 
 
 
 



 


