How do I update this listing?




                                             Broad RUN Investment Management is based out of Arlington. Broad RUN Investment Management is a large advisory firm with  More than 100 clients and discretionary assets under management (AUM) of $2,794,097,109 (Form ADV from 2017-03-30).  Their last reported 13F filing for Q1 2017 included $2,654,389,000 in managed 13F securities
    and a top 10 holdings concentration of 74.4%. Broad RUN Investment Management's largest holding is American Tower Corp., Class A with shares held of 2,435,591.  Broad RUN Investment Management has met the qualifications for inclusion in our WhaleScore system.    WhaleWisdom has at least 19 13Fs and  12 13D/G filings in our database for Broad RUN Investment Management. 
                                           






